However drilling down to my point, he meant there is a Kara in all the universes, but not necessarily on earth. Maybe a Kara died with krypton exploding, or maybe a universe where krypton didnâ€™t explode. He just meant there are as many of each of them as there are universes. Thatâ€™s my take on it.
